casebody.data:
No. 09-1443. Charles L. Ryan, Director, Arizona Department of Corrections, Petitioner v. Johnathan Andrew Doody. 562 U.S. 956, 131 S. Ct. 456,

178 L. Ed. 2d 282,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8063. October 12, 2010.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit for further consideration in light of Florida v. Powell, 559 U.S. 50, 130 S. Ct. 1195, 175 L. Ed. 2d 1009 (2010).

Same case below, 596 F.3d 620.
